            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "若聯邦政府關門 美國9月份就業報告或被迫延遲發布",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"若聯邦政府關門 美國9月份就業報告或被迫延遲發布\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"627\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RFf.EJxGlHxxyZemy__dbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYyNztjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-08/13d5b400-719a-11f0-bdff-fd9375344bec\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">若聯邦政府關門 美國9月份就業報告或被迫延遲發布</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
